| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7342 — Recovery Inhibition (safepay)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7ab42882-c5e8-5e96-a7fb-82b3f19a26ac"
